snippet.title: STRAIN - A Story-Driven Survival Game in a Neon Apocalypse
snippet.description:
============================================
🎮🎮 WISHLIST STRAIN ON STEAM: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1289570/Strain/
============================================

Please share this video with anyone who may be interested in the game. :)

STRAIN will be coming to Kickstarter very soon. The early access game will be available to backers shortly after.

Watch the development of the game here: https://www.twitch.tv/lana_lux
